## 执行约束

**严禁自动提交。** 只有在用户明确发出提交指令（如"提交代码"、"git commit"、"push"等）时，才能执行 git add / commit / push 操作。代码发生变更后，绝不允许自动执行任何 Git 提交或推送。

## Commit Message 规范

When generating commit messages:

- Use Conventional Commits format: type(scope): description
- Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore
- Title max 60 characters, present tense, lowercase
- Add detailed body only when needed
